		{
			x: 6.0d
			y: -6.0d
			shape: "gear"
			subtitle: "Now that's Pyro! Left Click form more info"
			description: [
				"The Flamethrower is a ranged weapon which uses Hydrogen gas as its fuel. It is fairly effective against mobs as it deals damage when they are directly hit with the stream and sets them on fire. It is most effective on large groups of mobs, where the user can hose down the entire group with fuel at a short distance."
				""
				"The Flamethrower has multiple modes. You can switch between them by using shift scrol. The modes are:"
				""
				"- Combat: Damages mobs and sets them on fire. Destroys any items on the ground. Does not set fire to blocks nor damage them."
				""
				"- Heat: Same as combat, but blocks/items that have a smelter recipe will be instantly converted into it. For example you can fire a short burst at iron ore block and a single ingot of iron will be dropped."
				""
				"- Inferno: Same as combat, but blocks that the stream hits will be hit with blast damage and will usually be destroyed. Nearby blocks will be set on fire."
			]
			dependencies: ["77407B54D3696E59"]
			id: "0ACB135EE44B6CFE"
			tasks: [{
				id: "0D7D3EA1AE3740EC"
				type: "item"
				item: "mekanism:flamethrower"
			}]
		}
		{
			x: 6.0d
			y: -7.0d
			shape: "gear"
			subtitle: "The Atomic Disassembler is a powerful mining tool, capable of Veinmining just about anything. Left Click for more info"
			description: [
				"The Atomic Disassembler is Mekanism's an all-in-one tool, essentially the ultimate, electronic version of a paxel.  The Disassembler will replace your Pickaxe, Axe, Sword and Shovel. It will not replace your Shears."
				""
				"This tool has more operating modes:"
				""
				"- Normal: Works as a diamond tool with efficiency II."
				""
				"- Slow: Works as a diamond tool."
				""
				"- Fast: Works as a diamond tool with effciency V."
				""
				"- Vein: Mines an entire vein of ores, or can chop down a tree with a single swing."
				""
				"- Off: Will not interact with the nearby blocks."
			]
			dependencies: ["20066A1C19E42D20"]
			id: "014A94BFD6243468"
			tasks: [{
				id: "1D5C7D64C3DCFE8A"
				type: "item"
				item: {
					id: "mekanism:atomic_disassembler"
