			x: 6.0d
			y: -9.25d
			shape: "gear"
			subtitle: "By default, the Meka-Tool will be almost useless. However, it can receive a variety of modules to enable a wide range of functions. Like with the MekaSuit, you can configure the Meka-Tool's modules from the Configuration Menu which can be accessed with the \"\\\" key"
